  "body": "\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nUsing `truffle develop --log` as my testrpc replacement, every 4 (or so) times of running `truffle test`, I have to exit out of the develop env and start it again. The error I receive is below.\r\n\r\n```\r\nError: VM Exception while processing transaction: invalid opcode\r\n    at Object.InvalidResponse (/Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:37872:16)\r\n    at /Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:316805:36\r\n    at /Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:164746:11\r\n    at /Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:294942:9\r\n    at XMLHttpRequest.request.onreadystatechange (/Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:296367:13)\r\n    at XMLHttpRequestEventTarget.dispatchEvent (/Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:164934:18)\r\n    at XMLHttpRequest._setReadyState (/Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:165224:12)\r\n    at XMLHttpRequest._onHttpResponseEnd (/Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:165379:12)\r\n    at IncomingMessage.<anonymous> (/Users/brianedelman/.nvm/versions/node/v8.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:165339:24)\r\n    at emitNone (events.js:110:20)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nRun truffle test multiple times without restarting truffle develop --log. I am running about 17 tests at the moment.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThe test should complete normally.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nThe test does not get run. Files are compiled and solc runs and gives me warnings about public declarations, but the error above halts everything.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: 10.12.6\r\n* Truffle version: 4.0.0-beta.2\r\nSolidity v0.4.17\r\n* node version: 8.4.0\r\n* npm version: 5.5.1\r\n",
